# App bundle / build zips must never be committed to the apps repo — the repo
# holds the *extracted* app files (apps/<id>/…), not the packaged .zip. The
# WordPress submission pipeline keeps the zip; only the unpacked bundle is
# promoted here.
#
# Note: this does NOT untrack zips already committed. If a real asset happens to
# be a .zip that must stay in the repo, force-add it with:  git add -f path.zip
*.zip
